WEBVTT

00:03.520 --> 00:04.280
Your Majesty

00:04.400 --> 00:07.000
This is this year's budget for all departments

00:07.400 --> 00:08.880
I have prepared a memorial

00:15.000 --> 00:16.760
The silver allocated to various regions

00:16.760 --> 00:17.880
All have detailed records

00:18.280 --> 00:19.760
Please review, Your Majesty

00:20.520 --> 00:22.480
Last year's tax revenue

00:22.520 --> 00:24.840
Totals 10.5 million taels

00:25.400 --> 00:27.120
The deficit from previous years

00:27.120 --> 00:29.240
Totals 2.8 million taels

00:30.000 --> 00:30.640
This

00:30.640 --> 00:32.160
Must be made up no matter what

00:32.880 --> 00:34.920
Frontline General Zu's military expenses

00:35.240 --> 00:36.720
This is essential

00:36.760 --> 00:37.760
Three million taels

00:38.120 --> 00:39.280
Court officials' salaries

00:39.280 --> 00:41.360
Total 1.6 million taels

00:41.520 --> 00:43.000
For Qiaozhou construction

00:43.000 --> 00:45.360
Disaster relief and settling refugees in Liangzhou

00:45.520 --> 00:47.360
At least three million taels expected

00:47.520 --> 00:49.240
Tax revenue is already tight

00:52.120 --> 00:53.000
I

00:53.240 --> 00:54.360
Will take the lead

00:54.480 --> 00:55.720
Deduct from my salary

00:55.880 --> 00:57.640
Try to squeeze out

00:57.760 --> 00:58.760
Two hundred thousand taels

01:04.840 --> 01:07.520
Then Your Majesty's taking concubines this year, palace repairs

01:07.760 --> 01:10.120
And various palace expenses

01:10.240 --> 01:11.120
Wouldn't that

01:11.120 --> 01:12.720
Only leave three hundred thousand taels?

01:12.880 --> 01:13.600
Your Majesty

01:14.120 --> 01:14.880
In recent years

01:14.880 --> 01:17.920
Defensive construction everywhere has cost enormous amounts

01:18.120 --> 01:20.640
Northern refugees returning south are also numerous

01:21.120 --> 01:22.880
Your Majesty, please endure this year

01:23.000 --> 01:23.640
Next year

01:23.760 --> 01:25.640
Next year I will definitely gather enough

01:25.640 --> 01:28.040
For palace and harem repair expenses
